+### 3.83 FR-E83: Safe Local Run Pruning
+
+- **Description:** `flowai-workflow runs prune --workflow <dir> --keep <N>`
+  prunes oldest terminal, unlocked `<workflow-dir>/runs/<run-id>/`
+  dirs until only `N` newest remain. Status/start time come only from
+  journal replay. Missing/unreplayable journals are unknown-state skips;
+  `--dry-run` reports only.
+- **Tasks:** [runs-prune](../tasks/2026/06/runs-prune.md)
+- **Motivation:** Manual cleanup can delete active or unprovable-state runs.
+- **Acceptance criteria:**
+  - [x] Selection, deletion, skips, `--keep 0`, `--dry-run`, bad
+    `--keep`, and help covered. Evidence:
+    `runs-prune_test.ts` FR-E83 tests; `cli_test.ts` FR-E83 tests.
